      "justification": "If confirmed, this is a minor concern about the evidential basis for the paper's motivation and discussion. It does not affect the review of methodological correctness of the formal work. The author is transparent about this (Section 7.6). The appropriate action is simply to note the reliance on recent preprints."
    }
  ]
}
